Privacy Policy

This extension, "Ruhuna SGPA Calculator," does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data from users. The extension operates entirely on the user's browser and only interacts with the page's data to calculate SGPA based on grades provided on the university website.

No information is sent to external servers or third parties, ensuring the privacy and security of the user's data.

For any concerns or questions about privacy, please contact: thanushanth.20@cse.mrt.ac.lk
